title.narrative: Support to NATO and UK military exercises

description.narrative: This activity (Support to NATO and UK military exercises) is a component of Centre for UK’s civil-military integrated approach to activity in/on fragile and conflict affected states. reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £463,063. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Research/scientific institutions. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-04-2013 and the end date is 31-03-2015.
